  </tr>
</table>

## 🎵 Start Listening!

#### Code.org is proud to have curated a set of popular songs for Music Lab that we know your students will enjoy. We've compiled these songs into a Spotify playlist for your listening pleasure! This playlist contains non-explicit versions of each song.

